title: Average retail price for white sugar in Canada 2015 to 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart represents Average retail price in CAD on the Y-axis. And, its value throughout 12 Months for 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and 2019.
All through the Months, the Average retail price in CAD for 2018 have lowered. On the other hand, for 2017 the Average retail price in CAD have grew.
Month May had the maximum Average retail price in CAD among all 5 groups, and it was for 2017. The minimum Average retail price in CAD was observed in Month Jul for 2019.
Among all the Months, 2018 had the highest Average retail price in CAD 271.0 in Month Apr and lowest value 27.0 in Month Aug.

max_summary: This grouped bar chart represents Average retail price in CAD on the Y-axis. And, how the value changed throughout 12 Months for 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and 2019.
All through the Months, the Average retail price in CAD for 2018 have lowered. On the other hand, for 2017 the Average retail price in CAD have grew.
Month May had the maximum Average retail price in CAD among all 5 groups, and it was for 2017. The minimum Average retail price in CAD was observed in Month Jul for 2019.
Among all the Months, 2018 had the highest Average retail price in CAD in Month Apr and lowest Average retail price in CAD in Month Aug.
The maximum Average retail price in CAD for 2018 that was found in Month Apr was 10.04 times larger than the minimum Average retail price in CAD observed in Month Aug.
Among the groups, 2016 had the biggest difference in Average retail price in CAD. Where the maximum Average retail price in CAD was 10.29 times larger than the minimum Average retail price in CAD.

In Month May, 2017 had the highest Average retail price in CAD 294.0 among the 5 groups and in Jul, 2019 had the lowest Average retail price in CAD 25.0. The second highest Average retail price in CAD 271.0 was observed for 2017 in Month May.
Averaging all 5 groups 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and 2019, the Month Jan is the maximum Average retail price in CAD and Dec is the minimum Average retail price in CAD.
